      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and stayed on top of every single service. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it! It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
