    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen delivers peak performance via individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS variable valve timing system, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis integrity is flawless, featuring preventative subframe reinforcement and a torque-sensing M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every mechanical interface remains tight, from the MacPherson strut front architecture to the multi-link rear suspension. Finished in immaculate Carbon Black with zero paint oxidation or interior bolster wear, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of longitudinal driving dynamics and analog tactile feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
