      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and strictly hand-washed since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, protected by a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather remains supple without a single crease, and it carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the adaptive climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. With such low mileage and a pristine undercarriage, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
